gn: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 140, 140)\"><strong>So why does he look at you like you're the last thing holding him together?</strong></span></p><p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 134, 184)\">-ЛӢЛҸ ај»</span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 173, 95)\">вқҒ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 134, 184)\">ајә ЛҺЛҠ-</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: c","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"RgI92GAF4uZ9Cy66UTVRL.webp","creator":"Alona Selwinae","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["рҹ‘Ё Male","рҹ§‘вҖҚрҹҺЁ OC","рҹҸ° Historical","рҹ‘‘ Royalty","рҹ”® Magical","рҹ‘Ө AnyPOV","рҹҢ— Switch"],"chats":51006,"messages":1255406,"created_at":"2025-03-27T19:30:57.643445+00:00"}